Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.96,0:00:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The history of games can be traced back...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the way to Ancient Egypt 5,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These ancient games decided the fate of the citizens and the kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They were called the Dark Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, the time where a boy has solved the Millennium Puzzle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and released the Dark Games has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A boy with both a heart of light and darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}People refer to him as Yuugiou: The Game King.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.38,0:00:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.83,0:01:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.97,0:01:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.22,0:01:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.02,0:01:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I expect that you will transfer all \Nthat you have from Kaiba Corporation to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.91,0:01:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We understand what you are saying,\N but... we have a condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.52,0:02:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defeating that boy named Yugi will be very easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.96,0:02:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba! Release Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you win the duel, I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the opponent for the duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.17,0:02:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's already waiting... Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(309,125)}Back from the Dead! \NMagical Silk Hat
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... you will now fight with Seto Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Against Seto Kaiba's {\i1}spirit{\i0}, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto Kaiba is not among the living anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lie! My brother didn't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:03:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a lie! He died because of his hate for Yugi Mutou!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, that one standing up there is only Kaiba's spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you going to do, Yugi? Fight or not fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. I will reveal that person's true self!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto Kaiba died?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That's what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! That is something so unlucky....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is an impostor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't please you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well... it's all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just watch this as entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me but, I don't really understand the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.74,0:03:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-boy will surely come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then he will be in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I lost to you, I lost interest in everything..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.43,0:03:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely unforgivable...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I stand at the door to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will drag you into that hell along with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can faze me with this spirit talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what you want {\i1}after{\i0} you beat my deck...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you have Kaiba's face and tone,\N you can't have his deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother would never get killed so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, don't listen to him! He's just a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The opponents you will fight on this island...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}are not just the ordinary ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the first one that the Industrial Illusions
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}sent to this island in order to defeat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You will lose your heart to Kaiba's spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That'll be your downfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When that happens.... Kaiba Corporation will belong to Mr. Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:04:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll bet three stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well! I will bet three... all that I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cyclops in attack mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.25,0:05:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the problem, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cyclops... that's really a card that Kaiba has in his deck...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother has that card in his deck too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, that doesn't mean that is Kaiba's deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No... I don't think this fake could have Kaiba's deck...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a fake too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use this card to battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician in attack mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cyclops is defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.46,0:06:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As usual you are strong... strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... somehow is getting very fazed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... I can easily read your mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you are thinking now is:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Maybe that is really Kaiba's deck...", am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. This is the {\i1}exact{\i0} same deck as Seto Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dead Kaiba is linked to this deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba is not dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe in such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well... Am I not right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believing is the best thing you could do...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.17,0:06:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have it, do you? Exodia?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:07:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you win without it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Against Seto Kaiba's deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jumped?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We will not need to lock him up now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Voice verification. Your name is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Seto Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Verification complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seto-sama, it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I was absent... what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A board meeting happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was the issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}50% of the company that was held by the Big 5...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}will be transferred to the Industrial Illusions,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}of Pegasus J. Crawford, under a certain condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pegasus J. Crawford has organized the Duelist Kingdom tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If Yugi Mutou is defeated, the transfer will be complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Pegasus...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He intends to take over the Kaiba Corporation..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Yugi has the great Exodia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So for him to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}According to the database, Yugi Mutou doesn't have Exodia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Any other questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen Mokuba. Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was invited as a special guest in the Duelist Kingdom by Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mokuba has the key to the company's secret files room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.79,0:09:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So he took Mokuba hostage...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll surely free Mokuba, but now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need to stop Pegasus's plan to take over the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi has to win no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.97,0:10:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a matter of time for him to find that I'm using this computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fight against time! I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.48,0:10:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, let's use the network to find the battle places...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Target: Duelist Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, it's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, here I go...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the dead one came from hell to reclaim his revenge on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.44,0:10:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! The Blue-Eyes White Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Blue-Eyes White Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:11:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be... that's really my brother's deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? Are you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's is really...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real Kaiba's deck...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means... that Kaiba is really...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you're thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kaiba is really dead, isn't it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can imitate Kaiba's deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one here is really my deck...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Blue-Eyes White Dragon, full of hatred,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that revived to get revenge on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lie! Someone say that this is a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.48,0:12:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go together to hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.59,0:12:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Searching complete. Duelist Kingdom has been located and targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which duel rings are being used now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.03,0:12:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Actually there are twelve duel rings scattered in the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... In these 12 places, locate where Yugi Mutou is battling...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.37,0:12:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Searching... please wait a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Access denied?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes. The data of Yugi Mutou's duel is confidential.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.72,0:12:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Pegasus... you have something planned, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.23,0:12:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi's duel data is something that you want to be a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well... I'll surely find where Yugi is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, let's force our way in...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:12:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The method?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:12:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The duels that happen in the island have their data
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,transfered by this satellite and recorded at the Industrial Illusions's main computer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Millennium server.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can use this and enter the Millennium system...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we will be able to find Yugi's secret data in the records.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hacking? Their security system will not let anything in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This entire system runs off of a virtual system...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who designed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.67,0:13:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would I do if I wasn't able to operate with this virtual world?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, without information, you can't do a search.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Yugi is in a duel,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a high probability of a Black Magician appearing in the battle field.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen... Search for a Black Magician...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.19,0:13:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Magician's data and searching program linked together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... now hack in the Millennium system!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:14:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Understood. First step, from the control room link with the Illusion Satellite 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change Security wall's virtual purge to stealth mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stealth Mode has been reached.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start purge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Purge complete. Illusion Satellite 2's security wall has been activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... now use the path created to do a landing in the Millennium system.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Understood. Begin landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:14:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Reached the Industrial Illusions!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they didn't find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second step! Hack in the main computer, Millennium!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Understood! Start hacking in the Millennium system!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not attack this turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of that, I'll make sure that your monster has nowhere to run...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a magic card... or a trap card?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician in defense mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, Curse of Dragon in defense mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I have predicted...this will be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Trap card! Seal Defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.02,0:15:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this all monsters in your side will be in attack mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as the Seal Defense card is on the field...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}my Life Points will only decrease...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Blue-Eyes White Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burst Stream of Destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse of Dragon is defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.12,0:16:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not in this room... how many left?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.83,0:16:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's still one... room 146.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.97,0:16:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no one dueling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enter the room 146.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It Froze!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reboot it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rebooted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Re-access room 146!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It Froze!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unknown reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Freeze is a camouflage...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems that I'm getting a response to something that is happening inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that there's a Black Magician in the field inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt... Yugi's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which method will you use?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The key-hole destruction program! We will explode the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.93,0:17:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That building is the materialized form of the stored memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Actually, Yugi Mutou's duel data is stored inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:18:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, there's a need of a password in order to enter it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Pegasus...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A place like a prison where you can't leave once you entered?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good joke, but it won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The password?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.59,0:18:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alcatraz!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No! I have no chance of winning?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba's spirit will be happy to see you losing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother isn't dead! Isn't dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! Didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That my brother would come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I believe... I believe in those words...\NI'll wait for my brother forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mokuba... I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba is surely alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I believe! I will not lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Silk Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:18:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I play this combo alongside Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of these silk hats is hiding the Black Magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... attack! Use your Burst Stream!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the chance of success is one in four...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? If you are really a vengeful spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and want to really see me dead, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, Yugi! That way he has a chance to escape from Blue-Eyes's attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.95,0:19:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Door unlocked. Alcatraz accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the real thing starts. Pegasus, I will show you my, Seto Kaiba's, true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.83,0:20:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What foolish trickery... just to buy time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what you want... now, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.97,0:20:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I will destroy each one of them! Burst Stream!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow Yugi escaped Blue-Eyes's attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he didn't get out of the pinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun's deck has 3 Blue-Eyes cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, Yugi will...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Blue-Eyes is disappearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone must have helped Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally the real identity of the fake Kaiba is revealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to be confused anymore! Beat him up, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Blue-Eyes White Dragon Strikes Back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:21:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The flask shines bright
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}waiting in the Science Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By rubbing our cold hands together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They will become warm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.66,0:21:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll shower all over you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.72,0:21:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will support your lonely back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.94,0:21:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.92,0:21:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:22:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because you're surrounded by a ring of friendship
